<p class="" style="margin: 10px 0px 0px;">Rugged Body is a Nigerian fashion retail company birthed to create a fun, vibrant and sexy space for all. We respect the Military, hence our pieces are created to show unwavering loyalty to the men &amp; women of the armed forces all over the world, however not limited to.  At Rugged Brand, we represent every gender, age, and size.</p>
